# .roadmap.disease_mi (myocardial infarction / 심근경색)

작성: 2026-05-07
구동: 사용자 directive `/loop 5m cycle 고갈시까지 진행` + 4-disease roadmap 추가 (옵션 C — disease-axis-orthogonal)

본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 myocardial infarction / cardiovascular disease 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + falsifier inventory.

심근경색 prevention/treatment scope:
- primary prevention (statin + 항혈전제, lipid lowering)
- secondary prevention (post-MI, recurrence prevention)
- acute MI (reperfusion: thrombolytics, PCI)
- post-MI heart failure (β-blocker, ACE inhibitor, ARNI)
- regenerative (stem cell, gene therapy — research)

---

## 1. Target proteins + FDA-approved drugs

| Target                | Drug                          | Year FDA | Mechanism / 적응증                       |
|-----------------------|-------------------------------|----------|------------------------------------------|
| HMG-CoA reductase     | atorvastatin (Lipitor)        | 1996     | cholesterol synthesis (statin)           |
| HMG-CoA reductase     | rosuvastatin (Crestor)        | 2003     | high-potency statin                      |
| PCSK9                 | evolocumab (Repatha)          | 2015     | LDLR upregulation (mAb)                  |
| PCSK9                 | inclisiran (Leqvio)           | 2021     | PCSK9 mRNA-targeted siRNA (1-2/yr dose)  |
| ANGPTL3               | evinacumab (Evkeeza)          | 2021     | LDL/triglyceride lowering (HoFH)         |
| ApoB                  | mipomersen (Kynamro)          | 2013     | ApoB ASO (HoFH)                          |
| Factor Xa             | rivaroxaban (Xarelto)         | 2011     | anticoagulant (post-MI option)           |
| Factor Xa             | apixaban (Eliquis)            | 2012     | DOAC                                     |
| P2Y12                 | clopidogrel (Plavix)          | 1997     | platelet ADP receptor (DAPT)             |
| P2Y12                 | ticagrelor (Brilinta)         | 2011     | reversible P2Y12                         |
| COX-1                 | aspirin (low-dose)            | -        | platelet TXA2 (primary/secondary)        |
| β-adrenergic receptor | metoprolol / carvedilol       | -        | post-MI HF (mortality reduction)         |
| ACE                   | lisinopril / ramipril         | -        | post-MI remodeling                       |
| Angiotensin-Neprilysin| sacubitril/valsartan (Entresto)| 2015    | post-MI HF (PARADIGM-HF)                 |
| GLP-1                 | semaglutide (cardio-protective) | 2024 (cardiovascular indication) | atherosclerosis modulation |

## 2. 5-axis cross-contribution

| hexa-bio axis | 기여 (MI)                                                   | falsifier link        |
|---------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------|
| QUANTUM       | statin-HMG-CoA-reductase + PCSK9-LDLR + factor Xa-DOAC binding VQE | F-Q-6-D-mi-*          |
| WEAVE         | atherosclerotic plaque-targeted DNA scaffold (foam cell uptake) | F-WEAVE-mi-*          |
| VIROCAPSID    | regenerative gene therapy mRNA-LNP (cardiomyocyte progenitor activation; AAV6/9 cardiotropic) | F-VIROCAPSID-mi-*     |
| RIBOZYME      | apoB / PCSK9 mRNA cleavage (mipomersen / inclisiran 같은 RNA therapeutics) | F-RB-mi-*             |
| NANOBOT       | clot-targeted thrombolytic delivery + ROS-responsive release | F-NB-mi-*             |

## 3. Falsifier inventory (entry skeleton)

- F-disease-mi-Q-1: HMG-CoA reductase active site + atorvastatin binding VQE chem-acc
- F-disease-mi-Q-2: PCSK9-LDLR interaction + evolocumab interface VQE (large-protein interaction; partial active-space)
- F-disease-mi-Q-3: factor Xa + rivaroxaban/apixaban binding VQE
- F-disease-mi-Q-4: 10-statin-class library ranking vs ChEMBL Ki
- F-disease-mi-W-1: WEAVE DNA-scaffold foam-cell-targeted (CD68 / SR-A receptor) uptake in vitro
- F-disease-mi-V-1: VIROCAPSID AAV6/9 cardiotropic delivery mock cardiomyocyte (HL-1 cells)
- F-disease-mi-RB-1: RIBOZYME PCSK9 mRNA cleavage in vitro (inclisiran-class)
- F-disease-mi-NB-1: NANOBOT fibrin-targeted tPA delivery + ROS-responsive release
- F-disease-mi-CROSS-1: VQE-ranked top statin + WEAVE foam-cell scaffold + RIBOZYME PCSK9 modulation = primary-prevention pilot

## 4. Phase plan

- **Phase A (entry, this cycle)**: roadmap stub.
- **Phase B (statin VQE)**: HMG-CoA reductase active site + atorvastatin/rosuvastatin VQE.
- **Phase C (10-drug ranking)**: statin-class library (atorvastatin / rosuvastatin / simvastatin / pravastatin / lovastatin / fluvastatin / pitavastatin + 3 candidates) ranking.
- **Phase D (PCSK9 + Factor Xa)**: 두 추가 target 의 VQE.
- **Phase E (cross-axis pilot)**: VQE-ranked top statin + WEAVE foam-cell-targeted scaffold + RIBOZYME PCSK9 modulation.

## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **statin 은 이미 multi-decade clinical evidence** — VQE 의 chem-acc 는 in-silico 검증; 실제 clinical efficacy 는 LDL reduction → MACE reduction (MERIT-HF, 4S, HPS, JUPITER 등 메타분석).
2. **PCSK9-LDLR interaction** = large-protein-protein interface — VQE 의 traditional active-space scope 밖. epitope-paratope partial active-space + UCCSD 가 ramp.
3. **inclisiran (PCSK9 siRNA)** = RNA therapeutics; quantum scope 작음. 진정한 path = RIBOZYME / RNA-engineering axis.
4. **regenerative cardiac therapy** = stem-cell / iPSC differentiation; quantum 직접 X. VIROCAPSID gene-delivery 가 entry path.
5. **acute MI thrombolysis** = time-critical reperfusion (90-min PCI window); quantum-VQE-design drug 가 대체 안 함.
6. **post-MI heart failure 진정한 normalization** = ARNI + β-blocker + SGLT2-inhibitor + CRT/ICD; multi-modal, 단일 quantum target 으로 X.
7. wet-lab 없음 — in-silico only.

## 6. Cumulative cycles

1 cycle (97). Entry skeleton land 2026-05-07.
